Background

		Mr. Robert W. D'Loren has been the Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and Director at Xcel Brands, Inc. since September 16, 2011. Mr. D'Loren served as President of Xcel Brands, Inc. since September 16, 2011. Mr. D'Loren served as the Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of IPX Capital, LLC and related subsidiaries from 2009 to 2011. He served as Chief Executive Officer and President of NexCen Brands, Inc. from June 7, 2006 to August 2008. Prior to NexCen Brands, Mr. ... D'Loren served as President and Chief Executive Officer of UCC Capital Corporation ("UCC") from 2004 to 2006. At UCC Capital Corporation, he led the acquisition, restructure, recapitalization and/or investments in various consumer products companies including Iconix Brand Group (ICON), BCBG, Converse and many others, with a total aggregate value of in excess of $1 billion. Prior to forming UCC, Mr. D'Loren served as the President and Chief Operating Officer of CAK Universal Credit Corporation from February 1, 1998 to 2003, where he pioneered intellectual property and whole company structured finance. He was self-employed for eleven years and conducted business at Levien & Company, LLC. He founded D'Loren Organization in 1985 and served as its President and Chief Executive Officer from 1985 to 1998. He served as an Asset Manager for Fosterlane Management, after serving as Manager with Deloitte & Touche, where he served diversified client base. Mr. D'Loren has over twenty years of experience in finance-related businesses. He served as Director of The Longaberger Company and UCC Capital Corporation. He served as a Director of Ciena Capital, LLC (formerly Business Loan Express, LLC and BLC Financial Services Inc.) since 1997. He served as a Director of Achilles International (also known as Achilles Track Club International). He served as Executive Director of NexCen Brands, Inc. from June 7, 2006 to August 2008. He served as Director or board advisor to Bike Athletic Company, The Athletes Foot and Bill Blass, Ltd. He served as Director of Candie's Inc. (now, Iconix Brand Group Inc.) since November 18, 2003. He is a Certified Public Accountant. Mr. D'Loren holds Master's Degree from Columbia University and Bachelor of Science Degree from New York University.Read Full Background




