WHO WE ARE



XCEL BRANDS IS ABRAND MANAGEMENTAND MEDIA COMPANY GENERATING APPROXIMATELY$500 MILLION INRETAIL SALES.


 READ MORE >









OUR BRANDS




























WHAT WE DO




Xcel Brands has pioneered a Virtual Vertical platform for its retail partners designed to create clear advantages over other retail competition by improving on existing fast fashion models. We deliver dynamic proprietary brands and maximize margins through an innovative Quick-Time Response (QTR) supply chain. Xcel’s state of the art design and merchandising capabilities create dynamic assortments from sketch to store in as little as six weeks, ensuring best sellers are identified in real-time and never out of stock.  Moreover, Xcel’s media partners and celebrity-driven marketing strategy provide a powerful cross-promote including 350 million households worldwide and 100 million social media friends of friends.














BRAND DEVELOPMENT









Xcel Brands' management and creative teams have the ability to acquire and/or create new proprietary apparel brands to bring exclusive product offerings to our retail partners.
















LICENSING









Xcel Brands actively promotes the growth of consumer awareness for its brands through a wide variety of licensed product categories and branded partnerships.
















MARKETING









Xcel Brands offers full in-house Creative Marketing services from photography and video content production to digital strategy, web design, and branding.
















SOURCING &
PRODUCTION









Xcel Brands offers "Virtual Vertical" sourcing and production teams to support the development of a complete collection-based assortment as well as category assortments and QTR fashion.
















MERCHANDISING &
PLANNING









Xcel offers data-driven Merchandising and Planning support to ensure optimally balanced collections which maximize bottom line results.
















DESIGN









Comprehensive in-house design services including: trend reporting, print and pattern creation, fabric and technique development, seasonal concept direction, product development, and real-time design response.
















INVESTOR RELATIONS





Xcel Brands, Inc. (NASDAQ:XELB) is a brand management and media company engaged in the design, production, licensing, marketing and direct-to-consumer sales of branded apparel, footwear, accessories, jewelry, home goods, and other consumer products, and the acquisition of dynamic consumer lifestyle brands. Xcel was founded by Robert W. D’Loren in 2011 with a vision to reimagine shopping, entertainment and social as one. Xcel owns and manages the Isaac Mizrahi, Judith Ripka, H Halston, C. Wonder and Highline Collective brands, pioneering an omnichannel sales strategy which includes the promotion and sale of products under its brands through direct-response television, internet, brick and mortar retail, and e-commerce channels. Headquartered in New York City, Xcel Brands is led by an executive team with significant production, merchandising, design, marketing, retailing, and licensing experience, and a proven track record of success in elevating branded consumer products companies. With a team of over 100 professionals focused on design, production, and digital marketing, Xcel maintains control of product quality and promotion across all of its product categories and distribution channels. Xcel differentiates by design.







